wiki.content: According to the Party in the USA Songfacts, this is the lead single from Miley Cyrus' first ever EP Time Of Our Lives . The EP is being sold exclusively at American Wal-Mart stores in conjunction with the teenage singer's Max Azria clothing line. The breezy summertime pop anthem features semi-autobiographical lyrics concerning Miley's move from Tennessee to Los Angeles User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
wiki.summary: According to the Party in the USA Songfacts, this is the lead single from Miley Cyrus' first ever EP Time Of Our Lives . The EP is being sold exclusively at American Wal-Mart stores in conjunction with the teenage singer's Max Azria clothing line. The breezy summertime pop anthem features semi-autobiographical lyrics concerning Miley's move from Tennessee to Los Angeles
